  "detailed_description": "Gem Deeps is an action-adventure platforming RPG with skill-based combat, <br>hand-painted art, and deep lore.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight Packs Of Enemies</strong></h2><br>Every enemy has a weak spot.<br>Hitting these spots grants you critical hits.<br>Scoring critical hits is crucial when facing bulkier enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/3cde5c61814e22c6bec9b41a4c8159b9.poster.avif?t=1658511298\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/3cde5c61814e22c6bec9b41a4c8159b9.webm?t=1658511298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/3cde5c61814e22c6bec9b41a4c8159b9.mp4?t=1658511298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Level Up Your Abilities</strong></h2><br>Find the right tactic for different types of enemies.<br>Enhance that tactic and make a unique build in the Skill tree.<br>Depending on your choices, you could rule over all enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/1afec0456fb18e662ee92db1994d7535.avif?t=1658511298\" width=640 height=220 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect Underground Lore</strong></h2><br>Listening to rumors of the Underworld may reveal some inside of this world lore as well as the local boss's weakness.<br>Runed diary, on the other hand, explains the Underworld genesis story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/99ecd43b99b8f2b303134f3bf7bf18ba.poster.avif?t=1658511298\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/99ecd43b99b8f2b303134f3bf7bf18ba.webm?t=1658511298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/99ecd43b99b8f2b303134f3bf7bf18ba.mp4?t=1658511298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Gem Deeps is an action-adventure platforming RPG with skill-based combat, <br>hand-painted art, and deep lore.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight Packs Of Enemies</strong></h2><br>Every enemy has a weak spot.<br>Hitting these spots grants you critical hits.<br>Scoring critical hits is crucial when facing bulkier enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/3cde5c61814e22c6bec9b41a4c8159b9.poster.avif?t=1658511298\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/3cde5c61814e22c6bec9b41a4c8159b9.webm?t=1658511298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/3cde5c61814e22c6bec9b41a4c8159b9.mp4?t=1658511298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Level Up Your Abilities</strong></h2><br>Find the right tactic for different types of enemies.<br>Enhance that tactic and make a unique build in the Skill tree.<br>Depending on your choices, you could rule over all enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/1afec0456fb18e662ee92db1994d7535.avif?t=1658511298\" width=640 height=220 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect Underground Lore</strong></h2><br>Listening to rumors of the Underworld may reveal some inside of this world lore as well as the local boss's weakness.<br>Runed diary, on the other hand, explains the Underworld genesis story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479830/extras/99ecd43b99b8f2b303134f3bf7bf18ba.poster.avif?t=1658511298\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://